"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Dental enamel defects in a child with celiac disease",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 432px; height: 282px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Dental enamel defects associated with celiac disease may consist of cream-, yellow-, or brown-colored opacities, loss of enamel glaze, horizontal grooves, or shallow pits.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
